体;color: #333333\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;page-break-after: avoid;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">研究和教学方向</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\"> 街道及商业步行街设计</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\"> 住宅及商业复合街区设计</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">城市设计</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">建筑设计</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">室内设计</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 20px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong> <span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\"> &nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;page-break-after: avoid;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">教育简历</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\"> 198409</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">－<span>198907&nbsp; </span>清华大学建筑学院<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>建筑学学士学位</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;margin-left: 49px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\"> 199109</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">－<span>199404&nbsp; </span>清华大学美术学院<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>艺术硕士学位</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;page-break-after: avoid;margin: 2px 0\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">专业履历</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong> <span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\"> 1989</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">年－<span>1991</span>年，浙江省建筑设计研究院</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong> <span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\"> 1994</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\">年－至今，清华大学建筑学院</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\"></span></strong><br></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px;page-break-after: avoid;margin-left: 28px;margin-right: 0;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体;color: #333333\"> 研究项目与设计实践</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><strong> <span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">一：街道和商业步行街规划与建筑设计：</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．连</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">云港陇海商业步行街设计（<span>199901</span>－<span>200104</span>）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">西安电子商业步行街设计（<span>199908</span>－<span>200001</span>）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">邯郸邯北商业步行街设计（<span>200006</span>－<span>200105</span>）河北省优秀规划二等奖</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">山东东营清风湖商业步行街设计（<span>200209</span>－<span>200308</span>）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">5</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">哈尔滨奋斗路商业街改造及河园设计（<span>200305</span>）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">．桂</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">林市兴安县商业街区改造（</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200311</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">－</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200402</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">重庆万盛旅游步行商业文化街设计（<span>200308</span>－<span>200405</span>）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">8</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;font-family:宋体\">徐州城市中心广场及四条商业街改造设计（<span>200405</span>－<span>200412</span>）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">9</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．福州茶亭街更新设计（</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200602</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．河北涿州鼓楼大街保护更新设计（</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200609</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．天津武清区商业步行街设计（</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200605</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．河北邯郸中华大街改造设计（</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200810</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">－</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200905</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">13</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．徐州沛县汤沐路改造设计（</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200810</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">14</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: 宋体;\">．北川羌族特色商业步行街设计（</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">200906</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: 宋体;\">－</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">201010</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family: 宋体;\">）北京市优秀规划一等奖，全国优秀规划一等奖</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><strong> <span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">二：住宅和商业复合街区规划与建筑设计</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．哈尔滨立汇小区规划设计（</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200506</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">－</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200510</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">．贵阳花溪商业及住宅区规划设计（</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">200602</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-family: 宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 20px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">3</span><span style=\"font